menu_items.name: Hamburger

menu_items.name: Cheeseburger

menu_items.name: Bacon Burger
menu_items.description: Our regular two-patty burger, layered with four pieces of crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon.

menu_items.name: Bacon Cheeseburger

menu_items.name: Little Cheeseburger
menu_items.description: Like our regular cheeseburger, just one grilled to order, hand-crafted patty instead of two.

menu_items.name: Little Bacon Burger

menu_items.name: Little Bacon Cheeseburger

menu_items.name: Kosher Style Hot Dog
menu_items.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled lengthwise for a caramelized exterior.

menu_items.name: Cheese Dog

menu_items.name: Bacon Dog
menu_items.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled with a layer of crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon.

menu_items.name: Bacon Cheese Dog
menu_items.description: Hebrew National Hotdog, split and grilled with a layer of crispy, sweet applewood-smoked bacon.

menu_items.name: Veggie Sandwich
menu_items.description: Freshly grilled onions, mushrooms, and green peppers, layered with lettuce and tomatoes, on a soft toasted bun. Or, start with the bun and build your own from scratch. Not a veggie burger.

menu_items.name: Cheese Veggie Sandwich
menu_items.description: Grilled onions, mushrooms, green peppers with melted American-style cheese, served on a toasted golden bun with lettuce and tomatoes. Plus any of your favorite 16 toppings!

menu_items.name: Grilled Cheese
menu_items.description: Kraft American cheese melted on an inside-out Five Guys bun with any toppings of your choice and grilled until golden brown.

menu_items.name: BLT
menu_items.description: Six whole strips of American smokehouse crispy bacon, two fresh tomato slices, mayo, and hand-torn lettuce on a Five Guys bun.

menu_items.name: Five Guys Style
menu_items.description: Hot, fresh, boardwalk style fries, made to order each and every time. Cut fresh, cooked twice, crispy on the outside and mashed-potato on the inside.

menu_items.name: Cajun Style
menu_items.description: Made to order Five Guys boardwalk style fries, with a heavy dose of Cajun spices. Unsure? Get the seasoning on the side.
